  "id": "RAW_156715",
  "title": "李继刚实测 Manus：上帝之手",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3Iq5jtleiUvbFV2fmUT2xQ",
  "date": "2025-03-06 07:59:04",
  "author": "李继刚",
  "siteName": "Founder Park",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <br>\n  </section>\n  <blockquote class=\"js_blockquote_wrap\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"40\" data-source-title=\"\">\n   <section class=\"js_blockquote_digest\">\n    <section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">编辑注：来自 Prompt 大神李继刚的 Manus 的上手体验，有一些实例。</span>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100031133\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/beea7894-b368-41d3-7805-f7ad098cab00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/beea7894-b368-41d3-7805-f7ad098cab00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(46, 204, 113);font-family:SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">Prompt</span></code></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px;margin:2em 0px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(224, 224, 224);border-style:solid;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">A quick sketch in black and white using the fewest possible lines to depict a random award-winning photography theme.</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">the taste of the image: focus on hands.</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">The sketch emphasizes simplicity and atmosphere, using just a few strokes to convey the essence of the atmosphere.</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Negative space is prominent, allowing the viewer’s imagination to fill in the gaps.</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(51, 51, 51);padding-bottom: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\">缘起</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Manus 来了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它让我想起两个概念：「抽象之梯」和「抽象泄漏」。</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px;margin:2em 0px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(224, 224, 224);border-style:solid;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“抽象之梯”不是什么新奇说法，这是语言学家塞缪尔·早川提出的一个概念，常常出现在各种写作教材中。抽象之梯的底部是最具体的概念，顶端是最抽象的概念。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们使用的每一个概念都处于抽象之梯之上。好的写作教材会告诉你，要想办法让自己的语言停留在上或下的其中一端，避免悬于中间。也就是说，要么使用最抽象、最具概括力的表达，要么描述最具体、最精微的经验事件。这对我们的概念抽象能力和经验觉察能力提出了非常高的要求，多数时候，我们只能悬在梯子中间，说着一些两头不沾的话。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">《关于说话的一切》（汤质著）</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px;margin:2em 0px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(224, 224, 224);border-style:solid;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“抽象泄漏”是软件开发时，本应隐藏实现细节的抽象化不可避免地暴露出底层细节与局限性。抽象泄露是棘手的问题，因为抽象化本来目的就是向用户隐藏不必要公开的细节。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">–Wikipedia</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我感觉的趋势：AI 的抽象封装越来越完善，抽象泄漏问题被更好地解决，留给与人交互的界面，变得极为简单直接。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这时候，人在这个界面中，交互什么呢？交互自己当前在「抽象之梯」的所在位置（理解深度）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对比与 LLM 交流和与 Manus 交流，感觉非常不同，用织梦师群友&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(46, 204, 113);font-family:SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">文君</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的表述：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px;margin:2em 0px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(224, 224, 224);border-style:solid;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个是跟执行队伍聊，一个是跟总包方聊。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">刚测试了一下和「总包方」聊的东西。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(51, 51, 51);padding-bottom: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\">示例</span></h2>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-top: 1.5em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Case 1: 漫画式讲解概念</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(46, 204, 113);font-family:SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">Prompt：</span></code></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px;margin:2em 0px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(224, 224, 224);border-style:solid;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成一个 HTML 网页，使用多幅手绘黑白漫画结合极简文字描述相结合的方式，从本质出发，逐层深入，深入浅出地讲解什么是「投资」</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成结果网页:</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://jtjmcawb.manus.space</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100000843\" data-ratio=\"6.696581196581197\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d7ffa552-fdda-416a-2900-c5f2ec7afc00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"936\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d7ffa552-fdda-416a-2900-c5f2ec7afc00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(46, 204, 113);font-family:SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">跟进 Prompt：</span></code></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px;margin:2em 0px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(224, 224, 224);border-style:solid;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">请保持同样的风格，生成一个新的网页，渐进式讲解「强化学习」的工作原理</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成结果网页：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://piupyygp.manus.space</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100000844\" data-ratio=\"6.898395721925134\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd724383-7fc9-49f8-7c67-947945865300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"935\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd724383-7fc9-49f8-7c67-947945865300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-top: 1.5em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Case 2: 动画讲解概念</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(46, 204, 113);font-family:SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">Prompt</span></code></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px;margin:2em 0px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(224, 224, 224);border-style:solid;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">创作一个 HTML 的网页，通过动画+文字解读的方式，深入浅出，通俗易懂地讲解什么是「强化学习」。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成结果网页：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://8000-iw0hhqj04qbil4051yc2v-3b13abc2.manus.computer/</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">网页结尾的小游戏是个惊喜。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100000845\" data-ratio=\"2.9\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/10334a5e-eb1b-4afa-fa2a-7c079e07b500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/10334a5e-eb1b-4afa-fa2a-7c079e07b500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-top: 1.5em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Case 3: SVG 卡片</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(46, 204, 113);font-family:SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">Prompt</span></code></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px;margin:2em 0px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(224, 224, 224);border-style:solid;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">https://ralphammer.com/</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;网站文章的风格，生成一个 SVG 卡片，从本质出发，深入浅出讲解什么是「意识」</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成结果：</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100000848\" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/65febac5-cd7d-4e8c-773b-7b58bc082800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"825\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/65febac5-cd7d-4e8c-773b-7b58bc082800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(46, 204, 113);font-family:SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">后续Prompt</span></code></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px;margin:2em 0px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(224, 224, 224);border-style:solid;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">同样基于 Ralph Hammer 的绘图讲解和简洁准确解释的风格，制作一个 HTML 的文章，讲解什么是「具身智能」</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成结果：</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100000847\" data-ratio=\"2.8361111111111112\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8d4383d9-eda8-47e1-714a-d84df0962000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8d4383d9-eda8-47e1-714a-d84df0962000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(51, 51, 51);padding-bottom: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\">感受</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们的大脑与&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AI&nbsp;</span>会不会形成一种「我们」的关系？不是我在「使用」客体工具，而是「你是我的一部分」「你我是一体」的共存状态？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们的腿，会不会被<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;「自动驾驶」「Robot」</span>加持，肉身的移动，完全交给 AI 来操作？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们的手，这个精密的器官，会不会被<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;「Agent」</span>加持，言出法随，怎么随？得有「手」去落地执行，我们会不会已经在今天隐约看到了「上帝之手」的影子？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "李继刚评测 Manus，展示其基于 Prompt 生成多样化网页内容的能力，并探讨 AI 与人交互的新模式。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "李继刚评测 Manus，展示其基于 Prompt 生成多样化网页内容的能力，并探讨 AI 与人交互的新模式。",
  "summary": "李继刚对 Monica 团队的新产品 Manus 进行了上手体验评测。文章通过多个示例展示了 Manus 基于 Prompt 生成各种网页内容的能力，包括漫画、动画和 SVG 卡片等。作者通过“抽象之梯”和“抽象泄漏”的概念，阐述了 AI 抽象封装的完善和交互界面的简化趋势，这些概念为 Manus 的优势提供了理论基础。文章还探讨了 AI 与人之间可能形成的共存关系，以及 AI 如何加持人的能力，例如通过自动驾驶和 Robot 加持移动能力，通过 Agent 加持手的执行能力，最终达到“上帝之手”的境界。",
